to sacrifice his bishop to save the game.} 1. Kd1 $1 ({Following either} 1. Kc2
$2 Rh2 $1 2. Bf1 Rxf2 3. Bd3 Rg2) ({or} 1. Bf3 $2 Rf8 2. Bh5 Rxf2 3. g4 Rg2 4.
