Ke1 $3 {[#]} ({or} 2. Ke2) 2... Rxg2 3. Kf1 Rh2 4. Kg1 Rh3 5. Kg2 Rh6 6. f3 $1
{Black can make no progress against the White fortress.} 1/2-1/2

