{[#]} 68... Nxb2 {Similary to the previous example, I can resign here, but my
opponent was in time trouble . I decided to check his endgame knowledge in the
textbook pawn endgame, which arises after:} 69. Kb4 Kxe7 70. Kc3 Kd6 71. Kxb2
Kd5 72. Kc3 Kc5 73. Kc2 Kd4 74. Kd2 c3+ 75. Kc1 $1 {I remember that my
