25. Rf2 $1 {[%cal Gg1f1,Gf1e2] The most precise move. White prepares the
future evacuation of the king.} ({After} 25. Rfa1 {Black can follow with} Nxh3+
$1 26. Kf1 (26. gxh3 $2 Rg5+ 27. Kf1 Qxh3+ 28. Ke1 Rg2 $19) 26... Ng5 27. Qf2
Rxb5 $13 {with more than sufficient counterplay for Black.}) 25... c5 ({
In case of} 25... Qg3 {White can play} 26. Kf1 $1 {when the king escapes. For
example, after} Nxh3 27. gxh3 Rxh3 28. Qd3 Rh1+ 29. Ke2 Rh2 30. Rxh2 Qxh2+ 31.
Kd1 Qxb2 32. Rc6 Rb7 33. Rc5 $18 {White is winning.}) ({The immediate} 25...
Nxh3+ {does not work either -} 26. gxh3 Qxh3 27. Rh2 Qg3+ 28. Rg2 {White is
winning.}) 26. Nxc5 Nxh3+ (26... Qg3 27. Kf1 Nxh3 28. gxh3 Rxh3 29. Ke1 $18)
27. gxh3 Qxh3 28. Rh2 Rg5+ 29. Rg2 Rh5 30. Qf1 {/\ Kf2-e2} ({Another
possibility was} 30. Ra7 $5 Qh1+ 31. Kf2 Qh4+ 32. Kf1 Qh1+ $140 33. Rg1 $18)
30... Qh1+ 31. Kf2 Qh4+ 32. Ke2 Rxb5 33. Ra8+ Kf7 34. Qa1 $18 *

