{[#]} 28... f5 $1 $132 {The most active defense. Otherwise, Black could suffer
a bit in the endgame.} (28... Be7 29. b4 d5 30. c5 Nc3 31. Qa1 d4 32. Bd2 $16)
(28... Qxb2 $4 29. Qa8 $18) (28... d5 29. cxd5 Qxd5 30. Qa6 $14 {and the
outside passed pawn gives White a slight edge.}) 29. f3 {leads to a forced
